// memory_allocation_techiques or mtlb memory partitioning techiques or ya mtlb memory_fragmentation_techiques for loading the programs efficiently into the memory(here memory mtlb "ram").
// memory-allocation-techniques mtlb memory meh programs ka allocation
// So toh yaha memory-manage krne ka mtlb yeh hai ki apnko bas yeh dekhna hai ki bas memory meh apnko programs ko load krna hai, so toh mtlb memory meh programs ko load krne k kya-kya tarike hai.. jaise memory meh apn programs ko contiguous manner meh load kr sktehh hai, non-contiguous manner meh bhi load kr sktehh hai..
// Continuous-allocation meh program-files ko ram-partitions(where ram-paritions are simply called "frames") meh fractions meh accommodate (mtlb ghusa) nhi sktehh.. and ek process(where process mtlb group-of-linewise-program-files)k liyeh ek hi partition ho skta hai,and uss partition meh baki ho jagah bach jati hai usko apn "internal-fragmemtation) boltehh hai..
// Yaha yeh contiguous-allocation nhi hai, actually yeh toh contiguous-partition hai,mtlb processes ka allocation toh partitions meh khi bhi ho skta hai...
// And contiguous-partitioning meh  continuous-process-allocation ka concept follow hota hai mtlb process process puri contigous-manner meh kisi ek partition meh hi jati hai, mtlb process parts meh nhi jati..
// Contiguous-partitioning meh external-fragmentation ka mtlb ki ram-memory meh space hone k bavajud bhi ussmeh kisi accomodable-process ko allocate na krpana ko external-fragmentation khtehh hai

